commits.content:
name: diaspora_delivery
description: Diaspora Delivery - peer-to-peer delivery platform (Phase 1 setup)
publish_to: "none"
version: 0.1.0+1

environment:
  sdk: ">=3.2.0 <4.0.0"

dependencies:
  flutter:
    sdk: flutter

  firebase_core: ^2.27.0
  firebase_auth: ^4.17.0
  cloud_firestore: ^4.15.0
  firebase_messaging: ^14.7.20

  flutter_bloc: ^8.1.4
  equatable: ^2.0.5
  get_it: ^7.6.7
  go_router: ^13.2.0

  cached_network_image: ^3.3.1
  shimmer: ^3.0.0

  image_picker: ^1.0.7
  image_cropper: ^11.0.0

  http: ^1.2.0
  intl: ^0.19.0
  uuid: ^4.3.3
  shared_preferences: ^2.2.2

dev_dependencies:
  flutter_test:
    sdk: flutter

  flutter_launcher_icons: ^0.13.1

flutter_launcher_icons:
  android: true
  ios: true
  image_path: "assets/icon/app_icon.png"
  adaptive_icon_background: "#FFFFFF"
  adaptive_icon_foreground: "assets/icon/app_icon.png"

flutter:
  uses-material-design: true
